review: I got my dental fillings done with Dr Supriya Rojekar. She explained the procedures very clearly and ensured that I was comfortable throughout the treatment. I would strongly recommend Dr Supriya and the Prudental clinic for any dental problems.
Excellent! The doctor is very friendly and polite. She made Kartikeya very comfortable. Explained me the problem  and the course of treatment in detail. I will definitely recommend her to others.
very professional. Explains the matter in detail and approach she recommends. Mindful of limitations one may have on account of pre-existing conditions. Very cordial.
